{"type": "article", "id": 8267, "title": "Cumulus 云朵香薰仪", "description": "", "date": "2015-04-09T07:30:58Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 3, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605234631oJ7GbPI3w1SsuQlr.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t法国设计师 Constance Guisset 非常浪漫，推出的这一款 Cumulus 云朵香薰仪也从头到脚充满浪漫的气质，“云朵”材质为无光陶瓷，看上去温柔轻巧。上面开设的小孔让香气缓缓溢出，不紧不慢，营造放松的气氛。产品搭配一个小盒子，可以盛放精油，或者就像设计师说的 “意外获得的宝藏”。<a href=\"http://www.constanceguisset.com/\" target=\"_blank\">这是设计师的个人主页</a>，感兴趣的话，不如来看看 Constance Guisset 其他的作品。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234629hAE3Plk1nzQL82K7.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.6627451\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606052346296vOnyPiZHjBIVqao.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.6627451\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234630zOPa6BxAd1H9JcbT.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.6627451\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}